
Intranet for Joinville Eau Vive - intranet.jevck.com
Webapp built using rack/sinatra and ldap & mongodb for persistence.
Uses lemonldap (web SSO) for auth.

Dependencies (and their tested versions) :
- ruby-net-ldap 0.0.4
- activeldap    1.2.1
- rack          1.1.0
- sinatra       0.9.4

Config :
- copy config/ldap_sample.yml to config/ldap.yml and adapt it to your env.

Running :
it's just a rack-based webapp. rackup, shotgun or anything will do the trick.

